{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HrwrXZ8b6jRZU7RXvJKBBC","type":"tool_result","content":"# Session Retrospective ŌĆö 2026-04-02 (Session 2: Story 1-3)\n| Metric | Session 1 (stories 1-1, 1-2) | Session 2 (story 1-3) |\n| 1 | Fix `codeharness stats` to handle missing session-logs directory | HIGH | Standalone fix or Epic 5 | Carried from Session 1 |\n| 2 | Fix `package.json` `files` array ŌĆö remove stale `ralph/**/*.sh` and `ralph/AGENTS.md` entries | HIGH | Next session | Carried from Session 1 |\n# Session Retrospective ŌĆö 2026-04-02 (Session 3: Story 2-1 + Full-Day Rollup)\nVerification is **54.1% of total cost** ($8.31 of $15.37). This is consistent with the historical pattern (53.1% reported in Session 2). Breakdown of why:\n2. **Proof format issue occurred for the third time today.** Session 1 had it, Session 2 had it, Session 3 had it. Three sessions, same bug, no fix applied.\n- **Not fixing the proof format issue.** Three sessions, same failure, same retry cost. This must be fixed before Session 4.\n# Session Retrospective ŌĆö 2026-04-02 (Session 4: Story 2-2 + Full-Day Rollup)\n**Story 2-2 was the most efficient story of the day at 15.75 calls/phase.** This is a 46% improvement over Session 1's deletion stories and a 15% improvement over the previous best (Session 2).","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01D1aPv265mgJjX6WrHHertR","session_id":"605a3302-c654-40ea-969b-1ce171500852","uuid":"f85c3673-6496-4e80-a086-9f444930e765","timestamp":"2026-04-02T19:24:18.040Z"}
